{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2011/02/street-photography/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/story/","name":"照片故事"}],"tags":[{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"扫街","path":"/tag/street-sweeping/"},{"name":"街拍","path":"/tag/street-photo/"}],"featured_media":null,"path":"/2011/02/street-photography/","date":"2011-02-12T08:21:00.000Z","excerpt":"街拍也是我一直想尝试的事情，别说看似容易的事情，却要有胆量去做，之前尝试使用长焦站在远处“打”别人，结果出来的 … ","title":"街拍宜昌CBD漂亮GG&MM","content":"<p>街拍也是我一直想尝试的事情，别说看似容易的事情，却要有胆量去做，之前尝试使用长焦站在远处“打”别人，结果出来的结果不太满意，长焦奇怪的视角总是把人“压扁”，严重的“虚化背景”把人物与环境分离开来，街拍的气息根本感觉不到，而且按照大师的说法，站在远处鬼鬼祟祟的瞄别人更容易引起别人怀疑。</p>\n<p>看过很多大师的方法介绍，塞上耳机摇摇晃晃拍了就走、掰弄相机突然抬头闪拍、避免眼神接触……呵呵总归是要胆子大了冲上前去拍。</p>\n<p>如下图片是从nextgen gallery相册中迁移来的</p>\n<p># 2011-02-12宜昌CBD街拍<br />\n## 旧博客迁移过来的部分照片，2011-02-12宜昌CBD街拍</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/2011-02-12street/20110212161439_DSC_0052.jpg\" alt=\"街拍#4\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/2011-02-12street/20110212161450_DSC_0062.jpg\" alt=\"街拍#2\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/2011-02-12street/20110212161456_DSC_0065.jpg\" alt=\"街拍#3\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/2011-02-12street/20110212161502_DSC_0092.jpg\" alt=\"街拍#1\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/2011-02-12street/20110212161513_DSC_0104.jpg\" alt=\"街拍#5\" /></p>\n<p>最后分享街拍大师的网站<a href=\"http://www.nickturpin.com/\">http://www.nickturpin.com</a>。</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2011/02/street-photography/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}